--- Part 4: LES formula check ---
  Since beta_3(T\v) = 0 for all v (at n=6), rank(i_*) = 0
  => H_3(T,T\v) = beta_3(T) = 1 for all v
  This matches opus's exhaustive result: all 1920 pairs have H_3(T,T\v) = 1

